{"tid":90163,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE Math  /M1 步驟分","createTime":"2017-01-21T21:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T06:49:12.000Z","uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"895ed663f25299327bf812a659c8834aee1f7d83","tid":90163,"uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:29:10.000Z","msg":"有時候有寫步驟, 但係寫得唔足, 咁樣答案啱有冇分?<br />\ne.g. 2016 q6a, 佢話 x-6x&lt;66-6 , 有method分, <br />\n但係我直接寫 -5x&lt;60 , 咁樣拎唔拎到分?<br />\n<br />\n另外m1, poisson distribution個probi, 例如佢要求less than 3既proi,   可唔可以一開波就寫 <br />\ne^-入 (入^0+入^1+(入^2)/2+(入^3)/3!) ?<br />\n<br />\n即係一開波就factorise佢, 可以寫少幾個 e^-入<br />\n<br />\n同埋有時候probi 好長, 可唔可以let某個數做x , 下邊嗰part就唔寫個probi啲數字出嚟, 直接用x代替  ?<br />\n<br />\n可能1999, sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a381c7e8028894281d62ea3b78a1ca32fc5e7f","tid":90163,"uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:33:22.000Z","msg":"2016 q6a marking<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pnlxtsz6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpnlxtsz6&h=f3bb4817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ne.g. <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yjnsfc1b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyjnsfc1b&h=6a5a9ce9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1086de2f7a612f57f86384b768ff2444d25d7021","tid":90163,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T21:57:54.000Z","msg":"印象中我個陣老師話答案岩就拎得足分<br />\n唔岩就1分都無咁解<br />\n所以除非真係100% sure岩無禁錯機既話都係乖乖地寫返啲step拎下分<br />\n我個陣係寫黎俾自己清晰啲睇 無跟到好足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多時靠step分救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b5a8e2e5bf7f4da7a4f618445cd2f6eea1698d","tid":90163,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T22:05:06.000Z","msg":"佢咪話putting x on one side 有一分囉"},{"pid":"eb66779f09b77eac4c720fbde4710957738fd259","tid":90163,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:15:04.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"ccd1cdf52a65e12bbbe966d00a05b97e853d6bf4","tid":90163,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:16:25.000Z","msg":"要懶點解唔用summation notation<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72dc51e42c9e5d7e741ad4f367ce1b9434e5a5db","tid":90163,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2016 q6a marking<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pnlxtsz6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpnlxtsz6&h=f3bb4817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ne.g. <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yjnsfc1b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyjnsfc1b&h=6a5a9ce9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nQ6a你直接抄條式後爆答案都有分，總知x on one side就得，再者好多改卷都望答案先，見你答案岩就比full mark，見你錯先睇翻上去"},{"pid":"ed1f7851c48ea164dc5eee6b959abeb83a657ea5","tid":90163,"uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要懶點解唔用summation notation<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你覺得我m1嗰個寫法有冇分?<br />\nmarking<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hyod5skb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhyod5skb&h=cbf6b7a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e30305cd0ab3d536f80bfded23a3f423f7158bca","tid":90163,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}